ish containing sauerkraut into position, place wrapped tenderloins onto sauerkraut, secure Varoma lid and steam <b>35 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>. In the last 10 minutes of cooking time, place a frying pan over high heat and add oil. Slice remaining 250 g onions and fry them until golden brown. Remove Varoma and remove simmering basket with aid of spatula, set both aside and discard contents in mixing bowl."},{"content":"Place milk, butter, remaining ¼ tsp salt, nutmeg and cooked potatoes into mixing bowl and purée with aid of spatula <b>25 sec\/speed 3.5<b>. Slice the tenderloins and arrange onto a dish with sauerkraut and potato purée. Top the meat and purée with fried onions and serve hot."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Replace the pork tenderloin with smoked pork loin, thick slices of bacon <b>(1.5 cm)<b> or smoked pork sausages.<br>- For a quicker and lighter recipe, omit fried onions and bacon slices."],"basicInfo":["easy","40m","1h 10m","4 portions"]}